PrecisRe-appointment of DOMINIQUE LAMARCHE, of Longueuil, Quebec, as a part-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years and six months, effective June 3, 1998.
